This app will show the user's current location on a map, then going to record the user's location over time and as the user starts to move around in the 
actuan world, the app will draw a line on the map.
So users are going to be able to track the path that they make over time in the real world. You can user this application if you're going on a hike,
a bike ride or a road trip and want a kind of recap and see what path you took.



Express API
npm install bcrypt express jsonwebtoken mongoose nodemon -> dependencias instaladas

node src/src.index starts 

